[18:50:05] <psy_kai> Error 108 (Headset not found) may be a USB / driver issue. Please follow the steps below to remedy:First, quit SteamVR.Unplug the Link Box from the PC and power (USB, HDMI, Power).Wait a few seconds, then plug it all back in. You may see more drivers install, wait for this to finish.Launch SteamVR.You may need to repeat the steps above more than once. You can try plugging into the same USB port as well as different USB ports.
